on     Sunday, 4:00 pm–4:00 pm       All Faculty Meetings          Faculty & Staff Resources   .       Governance  Data Resources  Forms & Publications  Online Learning  Other Resources  UIC Global Grad Direct         Graduate College Bylaws   Graduate College Bylaws  The UIC Graduate College is organized and administered according to its Bylaws . This governing document outlines the membership, purpose and goals of the UIC Graduate College with specific prescriptions for how these shall be carried forth.  The original Graduate College Bylaws were approved by the Faculty Senate. Amendments are first approved by the Graduate College Executive Committee, and then by vote at the Annual Meeting of the Graduate Faculty.    Graduate College Bylaws         Graduate Faculty Information   Graduate Faculty Information    Faculty & Staff Meetings    Nomination Form for Membership to the Graduate College Faculty    Graduate Faculty Listings         Graduate College Elections   Graduate College Elections    Current & Historical Election Information         Executive Committee Resources   Executive Committee Resources    Executive Committee Resources         Awards & Diversity Awards Committee Resources   Awards & Diversity Awards Committee Resources    Awards & Diversity Awards Committee Resources         Directors of Graduate Studies Review List   Directors of Graduate Studies Resources    Directors of Graduate Studies Resources             Graduate & Professional Enrollment Management Reports   Graduate & Professional Enrollment Management Reports    2018 (contains 2014-2018 data)    2019 (contains 2015-2019 data)    Interactive Dashboards         Graduation Lists   Graduation Lists    Degree & Thesis Lists (Requires UI Box Login and Permissions)         Office of Vice Provost for Academic & Enrollment Services Reports   Office of Vice Provost for Academic & Enrollment Services Reports    Application & Registration Status Reports         PhD Program Review   PhD Program Review